{
  "stem": "1918.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 288.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even though, when they put out the daily dead, as they died during the night, and they put them out in front of the barrack, so that the death commando could come and fetch the bodies and slap them onto this contraption to wheel them to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we found the dead bodies in the morning who were thrown out in front of the block, what do you think the first impulse is?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not tears or not sorrow for the person who's lying there dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That person no longer feels anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I on the other hand, feel the desperate cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what we would do is strip them of their clothing, and thereby you could-- you could acquire additional warmth-- additional warm clothing by having another layer.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did not strip them naked because then they would have noticed it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we could peel off something that could help us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or I could put my shoe on the dead body and get hers because hers was in better condition.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You do understand what I'm trying to say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] right along with that kind of goodness of-- of giving your own bread and trying to convince you that you're not hungry, that went on at the same time, stripping the dead body.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But even that was some kind of a-- or I-- you know, somebody might have taken off a piece of clothing and given it to somebody who had less than she had.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So side by side, right along each other, there were acts of greatness, great humanity, and great deprivation of the human soul.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of such, you know, kind of a bestiality that would appear to be bestial.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In truth, perhaps it was not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
